  "detailed_description": "<strong>liquid entry </strong><br><i>Let's transform into slime, collect clean droplets and purify the polluted world </i><br><br>#2.5D #Adventure #Side-scrolling game_Platform #Story_Puzzle<br>Exploring through puzzles, the number of water droplets collected and users actions taken determine the endings.<br>Let's gather water droplets using the ability to transform into liquid.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2770300/extras/c39ca334e1edd1797fd0fe9e4147a8e5.avif?t=1711452788\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>A future where the world's water is polluted and almost no life can live...<br>An experimental body was created to solve this situation...<br><br><i>But he runs away...! </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2770300/extras/9ecd080da31de59adc66108d4007c412.avif?t=1711452788\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>A boy who turns into slime.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2770300/extras/3564302431f507ed6257646853608209.avif?t=1711452788\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>Where will he end up heading?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2770300/extras/31f891f1bcdb52bdc8bafbc94b8190cf.avif?t=1711452788\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>People everywhere......what are they?<br><br><strong>The ending changes only through your choice...! </strong>",
